        heading: "Party Boat Istanbul — Food, Drink, and Entertainment",
        content: "A birthday party boat is only as good as its entertainment and hospitality, and the event plan should scale with the guest list. Entertainment can be as simple as a curated Bluetooth playlist or as elaborate as a live DJ, musician, MC, or full lighting build. Popular birthday-specific touches include a surprise cake reveal timed to a key Bosphorus view, a confetti moment, or a personalized message screen on the right vessel. Catering ranges from cocktail-style finger food stations to full sit-down dinner service, and the beverage plan can be soft-drink led, bar-service focused, or fully customized around the event. The best build is the one that fits how your group will actually use the deck rather than the one with the longest inclusion list.",
